Package entity

Class AppointmentRecord

java.lang.Object
entity.AppointmentRecord
Direct Known Subclasses:
AppointmentOutcome
public class AppointmentRecord extends Object
Represents an appointment record in the Hospital Management System. Stores details such as appointment ID, patient ID, doctor ID, appointment date, time, and status.
